{"tid":1969786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林正財：為了能DSE如期舉行  限眾令和各行業的停業令會延長","createTime":"2020-04-12T16:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T17:38:02.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"728ccb79cba18d15b71e8d603e02cf63b5df6ff6","tid":1969786,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"教育局已多次表明，希望文憑試（DSE）能如期4月24日開考。行政會議成員林正財認為，若要確保DSE開考的感染風險減至最低，限制4人以上聚會禁令很可能「無可避免地」延長。但他稱，假如直至下周的疫情繼續放緩，個別按照法例暫停營業的處所，或有「率先復業」可能。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，教育局雖然傾向如期開考DSE，但社會也應先得出共識，否則不宜硬推。假如多數公眾同意如期開考，相信絕大部份現行限制聚集的措施，例如不准多於4人聚集、食肆餐桌距離最少1.5米等，在4月23日後會再度延長，確保開考的風險減至最低，「考到一半，因為疫情再高企而半路停止，呢個情況唔可以畀佢發生」。<br />\n<br />\n至於現時12類需按法例第599F章停業的處所，例如機舖、戲院等，林認為，若每日新增武漢肺炎個案持續少於10宗，或有討論個別處所「率先復業」的空間。但他強調，任何新措施均需以疫情發展、流行病學數據為先，政府不會貿然讓某行業復工，「例如酒吧，暫時都難以復業」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200412/5ZGTIP4VQDP2FW2TTIVRUVRSRQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200412%2F5ZGTIP4VQDP2FW2TTIVRUVRSRQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj8wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=54cd6b45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200412%2F5ZGTIP4VQDP2FW2TTIVRUVRSRQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=0aca64d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200412/5ZGTIP4VQDP2FW2TTIVRUVRSRQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"1c60ed920d1946995f6748abfb3b072a6c194bd5","tid":1969786,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"又黎"},{"pid":"b7